/>
</div>

<div class="aspect-w-1 aspect-h-1">
<img
alt="Mobile Phone Stand"
class="object-cover rounded-xl"
src="/images/3/3.jpg"
/>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="sticky top-0">
<strong class="border border-blue-600 rounded-full tracking-wide px-3 font-medium py-0.5 text-xs bg-gray-100 text-blue-600"> Pre Order </strong>

<div class="flex justify-between mt-8">
<div class="max-w-[35ch]">
<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">{title}</h1>

<p class="mt-0.5 text-sm">
Wake up to the Ocean Breeze ushering you to a new day at our exquisite 2br beachfront Apartment at LA Mera in shanzu Mombasa. Collect good memories and share them with friends and family.

Features

Luxurious king-size bed
Stunning Ocean Views
Direct Access to the Beach
Fully furnished kitchen
A giant-size Infinity pool
All en-suite Bedrooms
